/*:
 * @target MZ
 * @plugindesc [Skill Movement Extension] Dash forward when casting a skill, then attack through the original system
 * @author CFpanda
 * @url https://cfpanda.itch.io/
 *
 * @param ComboDashStep
 * @text Dash Step
 * @type number
 * @min 0
 * @default 1
 * @desc How many tiles the player dashes forward. Used by all skills with <comboDash>.
 *
 * @param ComboDashDelay
 * @text Dash Arrive Delay
 * @type number
 * @min 0
 * @default 0
 * @desc Frames to wait after arriving before generating the original attack object.
 *
 * @param ComboDashLockFrames
 * @text Attack Lock Frames
 * @type number
 * @min 1
 * @default 24
 * @desc Minimum frames to keep the player locked after the attack object is generated.
 *
 * @param ComboDashDamageRate
 * @text Damage Rate (%)
 * @type number
 * @min 0
 * @default 100
 * @desc Damage multiplier for the attack released after dash. 100 = normal, 50 = half damage.
 *
 * @param ComboDashStartSe
 * @text Dash Start SE
 * @type file
 * @dir audio/se/
 * @default
 * @desc Sound effect played immediately when the dash starts. Leave blank to disable.
 *
 * @param ComboDashStartSeVolume
 * @text Dash Start SE Volume
 * @type number
 * @min 0
 * @max 100
 * @default 80
 *
 * @param ComboDashStartSePitch
 * @text Dash Start SE Pitch
 * @type number
 * @min 50
 * @max 150
 * @default 100
 *
 * @param ComboDashStartSePan
 * @text Dash Start SE Pan
 * @type number
 * @min -100
 * @max 100
 * @default 0
 *
 * @param ComboDashArriveSe
 * @text Dash Arrive SE
 * @type file
 * @dir audio/se/
 * @default
 * @desc Sound effect played after the dash arrives, before the original attack object is generated. Leave blank to disable.
 *
 * @param ComboDashArriveSeVolume
 * @text Dash Arrive SE Volume
 * @type number
 * @min 0
 * @max 100
 * @default 80
 *
 * @param ComboDashArriveSePitch
 * @text Dash Arrive SE Pitch
 * @type number
 * @min 50
 * @max 150
 * @default 100
 *
 * @param ComboDashArriveSePan
 * @text Dash Arrive SE Pan
 * @type number
 * @min -100
 * @max 100
 * @default 0
 *
 * @help
 * ============================================================================
 * ■ Plugin Positioning: CF Battle System Skill Extension
 * ============================================================================
 * This plugin adds a "dash forward, then attack" effect to map skills.
 *
 * It is not a follow-up attack after a hit.
 * Instead, the movement is built into the skill itself.
 *
 * In other words:
 * Skill cast
 *   ↓
 * The player dashes forward
 *   ↓
 * The attack object is generated through the original system
 *   ↓
 * After the attack object hits, damage is resolved by the original system
 *
 * ============================================================================
 * ■ Suitable Effects
 * ============================================================================
 * Suitable for:
 * ✔ Barbaric charge + one slash
 * ✔ Dash slash
 * ✔ Close-range slash
 * ✔ Melee skills with movement
 *
 * ============================================================================
 * ■ Skill Note Tags
 * ============================================================================
 * <comboDash>
 * Enables this dash skill extension.
 *
 * Other settings are plugin parameters, not skill notes:
 * - Dash Step
 * - Dash Arrive Delay
 * - Attack Lock Frames
 * - Damage Rate (%)
 * - Dash Start SE
 * - Dash Arrive SE
 *
 * ============================================================================
 * ■ Rules
 * ============================================================================
 * 1. The skill is cast normally whether or not there is an enemy ahead.
 * 2. If the path ahead is passable, the player dashes forward first.
 * 3. If the path ahead is not passable, the player does not dash, but the skill
 *    is still cast normally.
 * 4. Damage can be scaled by the Damage Rate (%) plugin parameter.
 * 5. This plugin does not change the attack object type.
 *
 * ============================================================================
 * ■ Example
 * ============================================================================
 * Skill note:
 * <attackObject:slash>
 * <comboDash>
 *
 * Dash distance, delay, lock frames, damage rate, and sound effects are set in
 * the Plugin Manager parameters.
 *
 * ============================================================================
 * ■ CF-BattleSystem Core Plugins
 * ============================================================================
 *  Required Plugin Load Order:
