 * 11. Item pickup log (icon + colors name)  CF_LootlogScroll.js
 * 12. Item hotbar helper plugin             CF_MapToolBarArpg.js
 * 13. Animated Map Status Portrait Display  CF_MapFaceEmotion.js
 * 14. Map UI HP/MP/TP Display Plugin        CF_HMTBarsBreezeShine
 *
 *  Optional support plugins (not bound to the battle system):
